steps.name: Given  The user is on home page of ds portal
When  The user clicks Sign in link for ds and enters valid credentials

When  The user writes invalid code in the editor Graph representations and clicks Run button from sheetname "tryEditorCode" and row 1
Then  The user should be able to get alert on Graph representations
